      <h2>History</h2>

      <p>Special Connections Academy was founded by a DIR®/Floortime™ therapist and the parents of Gabriel, a child with autism and intellectual disabilities. They saw the benefits of DIR®/Floortime™ through his experience. The <strong>connection</strong> between the family, the therapist and Gabriel was the engine that propelled his social-emotional development and allowed real learning. He was finally able to succeed and feel happy. So, they decided to make DIR®/Floortime™ available to other individuals and families in a school environment.</p>


