      <h2>Mission &amp; Vision</h2>

      <p>Special Connections Academy’s mission is to provide individuals with Autism and other developmental disabilities an educational environment that fosters socio-emotional, developmental and academic growth. The goal of our program is to collaborate with families and the community to enrich the lives of our students and help them live to their fullest potential.</p>

      <p>We ENVISION a community where the individuality of the population with special needs is accepted and appreciated.</p>


